efinition","text":"ad.专有地"},{"type":"entry","text":"sure [ʃʊə(r)]","headword":"sure"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.当然；的确"},{"type":"note","text":"◎sure enough果然，果真"},{"type":"entry","text":"greatly [ˈɡreɪtli]","headword":"greatly"}]},{"number":270,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"ad.非常，很"},{"type":"entry","text":"highly [ˈhaɪli]","headword":"highly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.高度地，非常；非常赞许地"},{"type":"note","text":"◎highly appreciated深受青睐"},{"type":"entry","text":"exceedingly [ɪkˈsiːdɪŋli]","headword":"exceedingly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.极其，非常"},{"type":"entry","text":"extremely [ɪkˈstriːmli]","headword":"extremely"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.极其，非常"},{"type":"note","text":"◎extremely important极其重要的"},{"type":"entry","text":"rarely [ˈreəli]","headword":"rarely"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.难得；很少地"},{"type":"note","text":"◎rarely if ever几乎从不"},{"type":"entry","text":"rarely or never几乎从不，非常难得","headword":"rarely or never"},{"type":"entry","text":"overly [ˈəʊvəli]","headword":"overly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.过度地；极度地"},{"type":"entry","text":"unexpected [ˌʌnɪkˈspektɪd]","headword":"unexpected"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.想不到的，意外的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎unexpected accident意外事故"}]},{"number":271,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"seldom [ˈseldəm]","headword":"seldom"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.很少，不常"},{"type":"note","text":"◎seldom use很少用"},{"type":"entry","text":"barely [ˈbeəli]","headword":"barely"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.仅仅，勉强可能；几乎不"},{"type":"note","text":"◎barely understand勉强理解"},{"type":"entry","text":"scarcely [ˈskeəsli]","headword":"scarcely"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.几乎不，简直没有"},{"type":"note","text":"◎scarcely any几乎没有"},{"type":"entry","text":"scarcely ever几乎从不，很少","headword":"scarcely ever"},{"type":"entry","text":"hardly [ˈhɑːdli]","headword":"hardly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.几乎不，简直不"},{"type":"note","text":"◎hardly more than不足，仅仅"},{"type":"entry","text":"hardly ever几乎不","headword":"hardly ever"},{"type":"entry","text":"merely [ˈmɪəli]","headword":"merely"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.仅仅，只不过"},{"type":"entry","text":"mere [mɪə(r)]","headword":"mere"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.仅仅的，只不过的"},{"type":"entry","text":"practically [ˈpræktɪkli]","headword":"practically"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.几乎；实际上；从实际出发"},{"type":"note","text":"◎innovate practically创新务实"}]},{"number":272,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"nothing [ˈnʌθɪŋ]","headword":"nothing"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.无，没什么"},{"type":"note","text":"◎nothing serious不严重"},{"type":"entry","text":"nothing more than不过是","headword":"nothing more than"},{"type":"entry","text":"particularly [pəˈtɪkjələli]","headword":"particularly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.特别，尤其"},{"type":"note","text":"◎particularly recommended特别推荐"},{"type":"entry","text":"particularly true尤其如此","headword":"particularly true"},{"type":"entry","text":"inevitably [ɪnˈevɪtəbli]","headword":"inevitably"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.不可避免地，必然地"},{"type":"note","text":"◎inevitably demand必然要求"},{"type":"entry","text":"increasingly [ɪnˈkriːsɪŋli]","headword":"increasingly"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.渐增地，日益"},{"type":"note","text":"◎increasingly popular越来越流行"},{"type":"entry","text":"invariably [ɪnˈveəriəbli]","headword":"invariably"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.不变地，总是"},{"type":"entry","text":"anyhow [ˈenihaʊ]","headword":"anyhow"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.无论如何，总之"},{"type":"entry","text":"whatsoever [ˌwɒtsəʊˈevə(r)]","headword":"whatsoever"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad.（用于否定句中以加强语气）任何"},{"type":"entry","text":"lest [lest]","headword":"lest"}]},{"number":273,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"conj. 免得，以免"},{"type":"entry","text":"not a bit 一点也不，丝毫不","headword":"not a bit"},{"type":"entry","text":"not a chance 绝对不可能","headword":"not a chance"},{"type":"entry","text":"not at all 一点也不；别客气","headword":"not at all"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词nothing"},{"type":"text","text":"1. That's nothing. 没什么。/小意思。"},{"type":"text","text":"当别人感谢你时，你可以回答That's nothing， 表示“举手之劳”；"},{"type":"text","text":"当别人向你道歉时，你也可以用这个句子表示“不要紧”“没什么”。"},{"type":"text","text":"2. Nothing matters to me. 我无所谓。"},{"type":"text","text":"当别人征求你的意见或看法时，如果你觉得没有什么特别需要注"},{"type":"text","text":"意的事情，就可以用这个句子来回答。例如，你的同事决定这个周末"},{"type":"text","text":"去野炊，大家正在商量周六还是周日去，问到你时，你觉得哪天都"},{"type":"text","text":"行，就可以说Nothing matters to me。"},{"type":"text","text":"3. There is nothing to talk about. 没什么好说的。"},{"type":"text","text":"有些问题你不想回答或懒得回答时，用这句就再合适不过了。例"},{"type":"text","text":"如，有人问你今天面试结果如何，你觉得自己表现太差而不想讲，就"},{"type":"text","text":"可以回答说There is nothing to talk about。"}]}]}